1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 23=

11
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,560
Old man,

12
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:49,759
show yourself and die!

13
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,000
Die? Who?

14
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,840
Murong Jinghe?

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:56,840
Xuanlie,

16
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,280
you're late.

17
00:00:59,799 --> 00:01:02,039
My men have surrounded this place.

18
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,680
How dare you set me up?

19
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,760
Even if I die today,

20
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,480
I'll drag you down with me!

21
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,359
You crippled my legs

22
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,920
and coveted my mother.

23
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:19,000
Today, we settle this debt.
Once and for all.

24
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,400
Mei Lin entered the secret chamber.

25
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,120
There are deadly traps everywhere.

26
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:49,879
After getting her out,

27
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,920
we'll end this.

28
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:05,159
You wretched man!

29
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,519
You killed my parents

30
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,919
and committed endless sins.

31
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:12,080
I'll avenge all of them today!

32
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:17,840
Chu Yiyi?

33
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:21,280
Jinghe told you her name, didn't he?

34
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,719
The moment I saw you, I realized

35
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,319
that your mother

36
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:29,120
was the maid who looked just like Yiyi.

37
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,439
Back then,

38
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:32,280
she helped Yiyi escape the palace.

39
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,360
But Yiyi died.

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,000
As her servants,

41
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:40,039
they deserved to die with her!

42
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,680
If you loved her so much,

43
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,680
why did you let her die?

44
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:48,080
I failed to protect her.

45
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,360
I just wanted Yiyi
to stay in the palace,

46
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,280
to remain by my side.

47
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,520
But I never expected

48
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,280
the Empress's jealousy to run so deep

49
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,360
that she'd kill Yiyi behind my back.

50
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:06,400
I poured the poisoned wine
into her mouth myself!

51
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,560
I avenged Yiyi.

52
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,479
Xuanlie...

53
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,360
Father,

54
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:28,520
you poisoned my mother
with your own hands?

55
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,479
My father killed my mother.

56
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:40,000
So,

57
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:42,680
every fight between my brother and me

58
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,159
was all because of you.

59
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,240
What do you take us for?

60
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:51,840
What do you think?

61
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,080
I am the Emperor!

62
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:56,240
And I'm also your father!

63
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,000
Do you think the throne is easy to hold?

64
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:02,439
So many in this world covet that seat.

65
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,240
One misstep,

66
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,800
and our family would be torn apart!

67
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,120
Evil deeds bring their own destruction.

68
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:12,520
Today, go join them in death!

69
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,360
Watch out!

70
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,120
Xuanlie.

71
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:34,959
Xuanlie!

72
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,160
Xuanlie!

73
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,480
Xuanlie.

74
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,399
Murong Xuanlie,

75
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:48,839
why did you do that?

76
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,079
Mei Lin,

77
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,800
my whole life,

78
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,720
I've lived like a joke.

79
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:58,040
I couldn't see anything clearly.

80
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,399
Jinghe,

81
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,639
the grudges between us are gone.

82
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,360
We're even now.

83
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:06,319
Don't say that.

84
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,959
Get up.

85
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,079
We can keep fighting.

86
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:15,879
Yiyi,

87
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,399
in the next life,

88
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,120
we...

89
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,240
Jinghe,

90
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,560
I did all of this

91
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,120
just for you.

92
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,000
For me?

93
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:20,900
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

94
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:24,120
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

95
00:06:25,980 --> 00:06:27,460
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

96
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:31,140
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

97
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,940
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

98
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:37,940
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

99
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:40,660
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

100
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:43,300
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

101
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:47,260
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

102
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:50,460
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

103
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:52,900
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

104
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:56,860
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

105
00:06:57,340 --> 00:07:00,340
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

106
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:03,740
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

107
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:06,540
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

108
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:09,580
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

109
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:13,260
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

110
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:16,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

111
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:19,720
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

112
00:07:19,820 --> 00:07:22,780
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

113
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:26,700
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

114
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:30,340
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

115
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:33,020
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

116
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:35,980
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

117
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:40,340
ظآزTwo hearts leaning into one anotherظآز

118
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,860
ظآزPerfectly, impossibly rightظآز
